client.model.map

Interface ICatanMap

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CatanMap

    public interface ICatanMap
    The datastructure that represent the Map in a Catan Game Domain: hexes, ports, roads, settlements, cities, robber, radius. The map is in charge of determining if a requested move in the game is valid i.e. if a player can place a road at a given location or if a city can be built at a specific vertex
